public enum CardinalityRestrictionKind extends Enum<CardinalityRestrictionKind> implements org.eclipse.emf.common.util.Enumerator
A representation of the literals of the enumeration 'Cardinality Restriction Kind', and utility methods for working with them. CardinalityRestrictionKind is an enumeration that specifies the kind of [=PropertyCardinalityRestrictionAxiom=] on a [=property=].
